cing the shampoo she now uses.\n\nThe final image changes to a clean product display on the tabletop near the window. Three Agree bottles stand side by side in a row: a pink bottle on the left, a green or teal bottle in the center, and a blue bottle on the right. Each has the white “Agree” logo running vertically across the front. The bottles are brightly lit against the softer room background, with the window light behind them and the tabletop reflecting their colors.",
